1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,380
The first few feet outside should feel calm, not complicated.
迈出家门的第一程，应该安心，而不是复杂。

2
00:00:04,380 --> 00:00:07,990
Smooth power helps every start feel more natural.
顺滑动力，让每一次出发都更自然。

3
00:00:07,990 --> 00:00:12,240
Steady support can turn a doorway into a real beginning.
稳稳支撑，让门口真正变成新的开始。

4
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:15,820
Because dignity should never stay indoors.
因为尊严，不该被留在室内。
